N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 45-6.3 - Exceptions

State Regulations

This Subpart shall not apply to amusement devices known
as bumper cars. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12

45-6.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
